channel.title: Comments on: Van Halen rehearsing “Everybody Wants Some” for reunion tour

item.title: By: patrick
item.dc:creator: patrick
item.description: having never been a big van halen fan, i have to ask: what the fuck is going on during the middle of the song? why the fuck is david lee roth making crazy motorboat noises?
